    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_8129698651086595085.png",
                "id": "talent60361",
                "key": "Surge",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Surge"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Randomly summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oceanid Mimic</span> (Prioritizes summoning a different type from preexisting ones, at most 2 types of Oceanid Mimic can exist at the same time in the summons area).</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Oceanid Mimic</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summons</span><br>There are 3 kinds of Oceanid Mimics in total, and up 2 kinds can exist at once:<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Squirrel</span>: Deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> at the End Phase. 2 Usages.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Raptor</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> at the End Phase. 3 Usages.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frog</span>: Can take 1 DMG for active character. 1 Usage. Once this effect is depleted, deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> during the End Phase.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/b94e2c26e1f09a4ad1c7ffc224f6f0ad_2873266454365431303.png",
                "id": "talent57329",
                "key": "Oceanid Mimic Summoning",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Oceanid Mimic Summoning"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Randomly summons 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Oceanid Mimic</span> (Prioritizes summoning a different type from preexisting ones, at most 2 types of Oceanid Mimic can exist at the same time in the summons area).</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Oceanid Mimic</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summons</span><br>There are 3 kinds of Oceanid Mimics in total, and up 2 kinds can exist at once:<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Squirrel</span>: Deal 2 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span> at the End Phase. 2 Usages.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Raptor</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> at the End Phase. 3 Usages.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Frog</span>: Can take 1 DMG for active character. 1 Usage. Once this effect is depleted, deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> during the End Phase.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/ebecad0f977c56c89680ec4012285ba1_4008995234067965866.png",
                "id": "talent96025",
                "key": "The Myriad Wilds",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "The Myriad Wilds"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. For each friendly Summon on the field, deals +1 additional DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/691eab78e5923e0f25d72843ef295e1d_2926679978410372753.png",
                "id": "talent6140",
                "key": "Tide and Torrent",
