                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/8b4c10db031f4656dd4b2c8d73aa800a_7444922875377003942.png",
                "title": "Hydro Mimic Squirrel"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p>Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7771007163073142705.png",
                "id": "talent69439",
                "key": "Hydro Mimic Raptor",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/c463e84467f23d8619f9cb815665fea2_3368156722758095071.png",
                "title": "Hydro Mimic Raptor"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p>Provides 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield </span>points for your active character. When this card's Shield points are depleted, it is not discarded.</p><p>During the End Phase, if this card's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield</span>s have been depleted:</p><p>Discard this card and deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4249193725492194234.png",
                "id": "talent38635",
                "key": "Hydro Mimic Frog",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/72565a324bfe5f1bd45b24dd92aa105f_843034248863653465.png",
                "title": "Hydro Mimic Frog"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_7062243675674097145.png",
                "id": "talent12746",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1351195889584467516.png",
